With Luxuria re-entering the global
market, I guess we're going to see
big developments in trade.

rows.label: tlk45350351_03_msg0002
rows.name:
If we take the opportunity to grow our
own economy, maybe we can work with
Luxuria to make some new products.

rows.label: tlk45350351_03_msg0003
rows.name:
One thing's for sure - things are going
to get plenty busy around here!
